{"tid":1157856,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就算被性侵懷孕，也要把孩子生出來！美國通過最嚴墮胎法案","createTime":"2019-05-16T14:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T10:03:33.000Z","uid":228346,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec5cf56f033007e22a7b1e4688554c8fc3f4d9e","tid":1157856,"uid":228346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"美國時間5月14日，美國阿拉巴馬州議會以投票的方式通過了一項新的墮胎法案。<br />\n<br />\n這項法案堪稱美國各州現行墮胎法案中最嚴苛的一項：<br />\n<br />\n全面禁止女性墮胎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGONHF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGONHF1.png&h=e7416c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非是准母親因懷孕而生命垂危這一種情況，其他原因去墮胎都將構成犯罪行為！！<br />\n<br />\n阿拉巴馬州議會的這條法案規定，<br />\n<br />\n試圖終止妊娠的醫生將面臨10年監禁，而膽敢執行手術的，將面臨高達99年的監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbmjyOa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbmjyOa.png&h=225ce01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在阿拉巴馬州眾議院以75-3的投票通過這項法案後，參議院以25-6的投票正式宣告了這條法案的合法性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dfPV1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dfPV1K.png&h=96d64125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（在阿拉巴馬州墮胎法案參議院投票中投了贊成票的議員）"},{"pid":"8f97cd7292b83852f775742fd75642d070f4b16a","tid":1157856,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14c68bb3188596d7dfd05d309f02a5d08b57053e","tid":1157856,"uid":191633,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"去到太盡<br />\n<br />\n反墮胎係好，但連被人老強都要生個bb出嚟，日後要個受害者點面對個小朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa0cca4b260d48cff88dc4aad1b797141d8dee3","tid":1157856,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f97cd7292b83852f775742fd75642d070f4b16a","tid":1157856,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy"